## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="bd1d5-158">Poniższy przykład kodu resetuje geometrycznych przekształcenia z `pgBrush` do tożsamości.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd1d5-158">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bd1d5-159">Zakłada ona, że `myPath` istnieje <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd1d5-159">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
PathGradientBrush pgBrush = new PathGradientBrush(myPath);  
 pgBrush.ResetTransform();  
```
